      "type": "add",
      "id": "1519ba96afc2b1a8",
      "item": {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "1519ba96afc2b1a8",
        "text": "For whom or which school level is this method suitable?\n\nThe method is suitable in school from about the 9th grade and then, of course, in adult education. For younger learners it depends on the learning group. Learners should already have experience with self-organized learning. With a younger group, they will avoid certain walking environments - busy streets, intersections, etc. But peripatetic instruction with children is conceivable even on school grounds, or on a sports field.\n"
